# docdb-filter-below-project

## Description

Migrated to a declarative `.rra` rule with a precondition (RFC 0090 Phase 2).

## Rewrite

lhs: (filter ?pred (project ?cols ?input))
rhs: (project ?cols (filter ?pred ?input))
when: is_bson_operator_filter("?pred")
